channel.description: hey guys, i was wondering if anyone else has this problem. i cant log into any RSPS for example recklessPK, ultimatescape, soulsplit. i tried deleting the caches and re downloading it and also re installing the new java update and restarting my modem but still no luck what so ever? is there anyway to fix this problem.

item.title: Error connecting to server
item.dc:creator: @firstchoice8 firstchoice8
item.description:
@firstchoice8 wrote:

Do you use any sort of VPN, Proxy, or anything that could change your ip? I’ve been seeing ppl not able to login servers because of VPN’s lately, it could also be your internet going slow, if you noticed your internet going slower then normal that is most likely the problem.
